prompts.frontCover:
Flat 2D comic book style illustration of a happy couple, Lao Lao and Jordan, for a birthday card cover. The scene is dynamic and energetic, with a vibrant cityscape background full of abstract, colorful skyscrapers and "POW!" and "ZAP!" sound effect graphics. Lao Lao, an East Asian woman with long dark hair and round gold-rimmed glasses, is illustrated as a superhero, striking a powerful, confident pose with her arms crossed. She wears a light blue sweatshirt (no text/logos). Jordan, an East Asian man with short, dark, textured hair, stands slightly behind her, illustrated as her adoring sidekick. He has a huge, proud smile and is giving Lao Lao a loving hug from behind. He wears a tan hoodie and dark maroon pants. The art style features bold black outlines, vibrant, saturated colors, and a subtle halftone dot pattern for shading, reminiscent of classic superhero comics. In the center, a large, stylized speech bubble contains the greeting text "Happy Birthday to my Favorite Superhero!" in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script. The characters highly resemble the people in the reference photo, capturing their exact facial features, hairstyles, and clothing.

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
